::Slag/JetV::
Slag walks into the secret chamber.  "Yes smash" he announces aloud.
"But it may not be Predacons" he says even louder looking straight at
Crossroads and the other so called Autobots of the future.

JetV walks out.
"Hey, the ship is ready for boarding but you may want to stay out till
Pacifix gets here."
